metadata.name: The Wickeds #1
metadata.description: The Wickeds are here to give their audience and lovers a flashback to the 80s, 90s, and 2000s radiant styles: punk, goth, emo, metal, neon punk and rock! Yes, we are going to travel through the new future, Web3. And yes, we bring the nostalgia with us! All the futuristic and AI designs are blended with the irreplaceable aesthetic of the "oldies but goodies.” The Wickeds are the visual form of the Vaporwave; a subgenre of the new world that has digital aesthetic with simple touches integrated with today’s trend. This collection opens the gate to the future and past meanwhile you are here experiencing the present!
